title: Three Identical Strangers
description:
Big announcement-- Tig and Cheryl have merch! Check it out at podswag.com/truestory. On today's episode, Tig and Cheryl take on the hit 2018 doc "Three Identical Strangers." Matthew Modine and Madonna come up AGAIN, plus Cheryl recreates herself sobbing at Les Mis, and Tig pitches a potential name for an improv troupe. *this episode spills beans* (tigandcheryltruestory@gmail.com)
